    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Mythical race of one-eyed men inhabiting northern Europel they endeavor to wrest gold from the griffins who guard it. They are sometimes depicted on Greek vases, fighting with griffins.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
